<Base title="Author" description="Meet Greg Simpson">
  <section class="section">
    <h1>Greg Simpson</h1>
    <p>
      Greg Simpson is the author of The Quantum Contingent and Quantum Time, techno-thrillers that blend real science
      with global adventure.
    </p>
    <p>
      After 37 years in technology, Greg retired in March 2021. He spent 20 years in healthcare IT, culminating as a CTO
      and Chief Technology and AI leader for a Fortune 200 healthcare company. He holds degrees in Business and Computer
      Science.
    </p>
    <p>
      He brings his passion for technology and global travel into his fiction and blogs about the technology and
      locations that inspire the stories.
    </p>
    <p>
      Greg lives in Colorado with his wife, Karen, and they have two adult children. In 2026, he continues to expand the
      series with new research, new places, and new adventures.
    </p>
